### --------------------------
### GAMER — PARTIDAS
### --------------------------

### Crear partida estándar (4x5)
POST http://localhost:8002/gamer/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Mi partida estándar"
}

### Crear partida personalizada (lineal 1x10)
POST http://localhost:8002/gamer/games
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Mi partida 1x10",
  "filas": 1,
  "columnas": 10
}

### Consultar estado de una partida (cambia :id)
GET http://localhost:8002/gamer/games/1

### Destapar casilla (0,0) en la partida :id
POST http://localhost:8002/gamer/games/1/reveal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cordX": 0,
  "cordY": 0
}

### Destapar casilla (0,1)
POST http://localhost:8002/gamer/games/1/reveal
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cordX": 0,
  "cordY": 1
}

### Rendirse en la partida :id
POST http://localhost:8002/gamer/games/1/surrender

### --------------------------
### ADMIN (requiere login como admin)
### --------------------------

### Login admin
POST http://localhost:8002/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Listar usuarios
GET http://localhost:8002/admin/users

### Crear usuario (admin)
POST http://localhost:8002/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "otro@demo.com",
  "password": "changeme",
  "role": "player"
}

### Cambiar rol a admin (id = 2 de ejemplo)
PATCH http://localhost:8002/admin/users/2/role
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

### (Alternativa si tu cliente no soporta PATCH) via _method
POST http://localhost:8002/admin/users/2/role?_method=PATCH
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "admin"
}

### Eliminar usuario (id = 3 de ejemplo)
DELETE http://localhost:8002/admin/users/3

### (Alternativa via _method)
POST http://localhost:8002/admin/users/3?_method=DELETE
